    "description": {
      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t<p><i>Prerequisites: 4th level, @feat[strike of the giants|BGG|strike of the giants (cloud strike)]</i></p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You've manifested the confounding magic emblematic of cloud giants, granting you the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Ability Score Increase.\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Ability Score Increase.</span> Increase your Strength, Constitution, or Charisma by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Cloudy Escape\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Cloudy Escape.</span> When a creature you can see hits you with an attack roll, you can use your reaction to give yourself resistance to that attack's damage. You then teleport to an unoccupied space that you can see within 30 feet of yourself. You can use this reaction a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p></li></ul></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
